detail.description: The Mode of One heavyweight knit track jacket has a bomber silhouette and soft feel. Details include a ribbed-knit hem, cuffs, and baseball collar. ABOUT THE BRAND: Mode of One is designed for the individual who sees style as a powerful tool for self-expression.
